<% provide(:title, "About") %>
<h1>About</h1>


<div class="row justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-8">
    <p class = "h2">Overview</p>
    <p class="text-justify">This project is developed in partial fulfillment of the requirements of Server Side Development module in Software Development program in National College of Ireland</p>
    <p class="text-justify">The main objective of this mini-project is to develop a Customer Support application for the Sports domain which operates on the Customer-Cases entity relationship</p>

    <p class = "h2 mt-4">Features</p>
    <div class="row card-deck justify-content-center mt-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-3" style="max-width: 18rem;">
            <div class="card-header">Server Side</div>
            <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Ruby on Rails</h5>
            <p class="card-text">The application is running on top of Ruby on Rails framework and using Postgres in deployment</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-light mb-3" style="max-width: 18rem;">
            <div class="card-header">User Authentication</div>
            <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Sign Up and Login</h5>
            <p class="card-text">The user authentication is implemented by using bscrypt gem and by leveraging proper session management</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-light mb-3" style="max-width: 18rem;">
            <div class="card-header">Front End</div>
            <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Bootstrap</h5>
            <p class="card-text">The front end styles use the Bootstrap framework and plain CSS.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class = "h2 mt-4">Assignment Progress</p>
