    <p class = "h2 mt-4">Personal Notes on Advanced Login</p>
    <p class="text-justify">Step 1: Create a remember token for the customer</p>
    <p class="text-justify">Step 2: Create a digest out of the remember token and add the digest to the database</p>
    <p class="text-justify">Step 3: Send the remember token to browser cookie</p>
    <p class="text-justify">Step 3: Send the encrypted user id to browser cookie</p>

    <p class = "h2 mt-4">Other Notes</p>
    <p class="text-justify">Additional Gem 1:Used <strong>will_paginate</strong> to add pagination to customers and cases</p>
